<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_5d552bf5-65da-4b78-ac3e-d4595efa5196" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>C4D9</sptc><title id="_a51a86a2-1211-418e-8d16-715087be3ba9">Openings in fire-isolated exits</title><archive-num>2019: C3.8</archive-num><subclause id="_c1586c66-e882-4ad4-b6b4-65eb4e175b73" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_c994c0b0-fa12-495e-9ec8-e54fcbdc979d">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Doorways that open to <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1285_2.1.0.xml#_c71e675e-d6e1-4612-8e59-381a56e224a8" id="_66b0eb95-f95e-4aec-9741-fd6472759e10" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">fire-isolated stairways</xref>, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1283_2.0.0.xml#_2f0af1de-a7c1-44b9-a8b5-1faaedfdb023" id="_583e2aec-4a0b-4e6a-98f8-aa13aa5de71d" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">fire-isolated passageways</xref> or <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1284_2.0.0.xml#_cfa6cc89-aa6c-4eaf-90e6-8aabe04b9c76" id="_7ac4215a-2a20-482c-960e-4ca371e67ea6" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">fire-isolated ramps</xref>, and are not doorways opening to a road or <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1385_0.4.0.xml#_b4a20ca6-0197-4381-9e50-85c757fa574f" id="_893fd468-b6cb-4ae3-8f4c-0e78a21b8153" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">open space</xref>, must be protected by â€“/60/30 fire doors that are <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1449_26.3.0.xml#_7f0d37c8-f244-4a83-9a76-6ece85e1e430" id="_7ab1f4f2-b320-4efd-8326-7727b54d92d8" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">self-closing</xref>, or <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1199_0.7.0.xml#_ac370c9b-7389-4daa-ac5b-338e11dc43e7" id="_da87204b-92dc-4281-9742-14a2515abf9f" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">automatic</xref> closing in accordance with (2) and (3).</p></subclause><subclause id="_ce8c48bc-d87d-4014-9ccb-0c3303d52aa0" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_0768d181-0482-4b4a-ac31-a9edabd55a61">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>The <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1199_0.7.0.xml#_ac370c9b-7389-4daa-ac5b-338e11dc43e7" id="_f9e9e4bf-02dd-4213-8e69-ea9b737478c1" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">automatic</xref>-closing operation <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_28f43bd5-aead-4706-a7ea-7f3c6a54a673" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> by (1) must be initiated by the activation of a smoke detector, or any other detector deemed suitable in accordance with AS 1670.1 if smoke detectors are unsuitable in the atmosphere, installed in accordance with the relevant provisions of AS 1670.1 and located not more than 1.5 m horizontal distance from the approach side of the doorway.</p></subclause><subclause id="_579921fa-3e69-4e58-8158-dc26d8b29846" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_cd93afd1-f2c9-4b6f-a894-142f96157286">SubClause</title><num>3</num><p>Where any other <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_3a6d8527-f8b0-43a2-845b-e9a3ef03817e" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> suitable fire alarm system, including a sprinkler system (other than a FPAA101D system) complying with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/167_0.8.0.xml#_481171d2-3952-490d-b64d-c3d3f5d7825a" id="_3b325e17-a76a-468d-8f79-f21ac7592690" scope="local" type="specification">Specification 17</xref>, is installed in the building, activation of the system must also initiate the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1199_0.7.0.xml#_ac370c9b-7389-4daa-ac5b-338e11dc43e7" id="_d0e3df2b-96c6-4deb-ab5b-5a7b25ba0157" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">automatic</xref>-closing operation.</p></subclause><subclause id="_33e38ad1-5069-4c4e-a6ba-757685a75f63" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_61484a21-c4e2-4320-89a5-3608ea03b84d">SubClause</title><num>4</num><p>A <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1525_29.1.0.xml#_48631093-d96b-4a40-a86d-7ffae028f24d" id="_fa9182d0-44c6-497c-8ea6-ea77ca4a74bc" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">window</xref> in an <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1267_2.3.0.xml#_d87c7cc0-d0b0-40ab-9a5b-d070ed6e115e" id="_ddb5b9e1-4a5a-40e2-a6e0-d689021a8fdf" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">external wall</xref> of a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1285_2.1.0.xml#_c71e675e-d6e1-4612-8e59-381a56e224a8" id="_a72d427b-1a69-4597-a967-9597b2290476" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">fire-isolated stairway</xref>, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1283_2.0.0.xml#_2f0af1de-a7c1-44b9-a8b5-1faaedfdb023" id="_e96a2415-a563-4016-baad-4495887cc022" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">fire-isolated passageway</xref> or <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1284_2.0.0.xml#_cfa6cc89-aa6c-4eaf-90e6-8aabe04b9c76" id="_7d7afb29-7232-4426-8ee2-fc08d3f272f2" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">fire-isolated ramp</xref> must be protected in accordance with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1329_1.2.0.xml#_145deef2-6101-494c-89a7-a771d714af1d" id="_0a6bac42-6b05-42f8-9503-3761481b5790" scope="local" type="clause">C4D5</xref> if it is within 6 m of, and exposed to, a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1525_29.1.0.xml#_48631093-d96b-4a40-a86d-7ffae028f24d" id="_05a90666-6281-4117-889b-3103a7326816" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">window</xref> or other opening in a wall of the same building, other than in the same fire-isolated enclosure.</p></subclause></clause>